Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:52.03,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.95,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}虽然害怕…但还是想！
